<p><a href="https://www.v2dao.com/contents/xiao-yuan-mo-ni-2fUx/reader/1" style="color: #fff; background: #3498db; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 1em; font-weight: 500; text-decoration: none; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); display: inline-block; margin: 5px;">开学日将优等生能代调教成专属肉便器，在寝室与正宫吾妻修罗场，夜晚更逼她穿上紧身校服吞下存货</a>
